Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Smiley Ratliff's escape bid, 1984
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xcfk
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 11 Mar 1984
British government foils attempt by US millionaire Smiley Ratliff to buy his own Pacific island. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less